      • getClassWithRoom

        public Class getClassWithRoom​(java.lang.String roomName)
        Returning a class that has the classRoom that is specified as a parameter. The method loops through all the Class object inside the ArrayList and compares the classRoom variable to the given room's name. If there is a match, it is returned.
        Parameters:
        roomName - the classroom's name
        Returns:
        Class object in case of a match, otherwise null.

      • getClass

        public Class getClass​(java.lang.String className)

        Parameters:

        Returns:
        Class object that has the same name as the parameter. If not found null.
